Author: nak
Version: 1.0
License: GPL-3
Title: Association mapping using Gaussina process regression model
Description: Estimate and apply age- or time-varying polygenic scores using Gaussian process models. The package provides tools for modelling non-linear genetic effects across developmental or longitudinal trajectories, deriving dynamic SNP weights, and computing individual-level dynamic PGS at arbitrary time points.
